longBusinessSummary: Huntington Exploration Inc. engages in the mineral exploration activities. The company was formerly known as Goldust Mines Ltd. and changed its name to Huntington Exploration Inc. in July 1997. Huntington Exploration Inc. was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
